  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Creating these prompts required a tremendous amount of prompt engineering as they strug- gled to follow the prompt format (Xia et al., 2024).",
    "We first generate the question or the hypothesis and then re-prompt the model to produce the answer.",
    "For question answering tasks, we prepend the question as the prompt followed by the unannotated text to generate the output.",
    "For the NLI datasets, we use five prompt templates from the ANLI dataset in Bach et al. (2022) and plug in the hypothesis and the unannotated text as the input to the model to generate the answer.",
    "We use the same input and output to adapt the pretrained and instruction tuned models."
  ],
